{"id": "art-285", "label": "Art. 285", "title": "Art. 285: Evadarea", "slug": "art-285", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 285: Evadarea </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Evadarea din starea legal&#259;\nde re&#355;inere sau de de&#355;inere se pedepse&#351;te cu închisoarea de la 6\nluni la 3 ani.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Când evadarea este\ns&#259;vâr&#351;it&#259; prin folosire de violen&#355;e sau arme, pedeapsa este\nînchisoarea de la unu la 5 ani &#351;i interzicerea exercit&#259;rii unor\ndrepturi.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>Se consider&#259; evadare:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)neprezentarea\nnejustificat&#259; a persoanei condamnate la locul de de&#355;inere, la\nexpirarea perioadei în care s-a aflat legal în stare de libertate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)p&#259;r&#259;sirea,\nf&#259;r&#259; autorizare, de c&#259;tre persoana condamnat&#259;, a locului de\nmunc&#259;, aflat în exteriorul locului de de&#355;inere.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1394612760\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1165\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1394612760\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)înc&#259;lcarea de c&#259;tre persoana aflat&#259; în arest\nla domiciliu a obliga&#355;iei de a nu p&#259;r&#259;si imobilul ori\nnerespectarea de c&#259;tre aceasta a itinerarului sau condi&#355;iilor de\ndeplasare, stabilite potrivit legii.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1877252421\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1164\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1877252421\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3<sup>1</sup>)Se consider&#259; evadare &#351;i fapta\npersoanei condamnate la pedeapsa deten&#355;iunii pe via&#355;&#259; sau la\npedeapsa închisorii de a nu se prezenta la organul de poli&#355;ie în vederea\npunerii în executare a mandatului de executare a pedepsei în termen de 7 zile\nde la data la care a r&#259;mas definitiv&#259; hot&#259;rârea prin care sa\ndispus executarea pedepsei.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_245229373\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1163\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_245229373\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)În situa&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la alin. (1), (2),\nalin. (3) lit. a) &#351;i b) &#351;i alin. (3<sup>1</sup>), pedeapsa\naplicat&#259; pentru infrac&#355;iunea de evadare se adaug&#259; la pedeapsa\nr&#259;mas&#259; neexecutat&#259; la data evad&#259;rii.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_140245474\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1162\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_140245474\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4<sup>1</sup>)În situa&#355;ia prev&#259;zut&#259; la\nalin. (3) lit. c), se aplic&#259; regulile privind concursul de\ninfrac&#355;iuni.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(5)Tentativa la infrac&#355;iunile\nprev&#259;zute în alin. (1) &#351;i alin. (2) se pedepse&#351;te.</span></p>"}